                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d359">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to Minister
                            <persName type="to">Dawson</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1909-02-09">
                            <hi rend="italic">February 9, 1909</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Department officially advised that Panama National Assembly has ratified without
                    amendment treaties between United States and Panama and Panama and Colombia. Use
                    your best endeavors to urge Colombia to take similar action regarding her
                    treaties with the United States and with Panama.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Bacon.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
